title: Windows Server 2008 - Standard/Enterprise/Datacenter - 32bit - E
description:
This is a full installation disk for Windows Server 2008. (Not Alpha or Beta)
You can install Standard, Enterprise, or Datacenter edition as 32bit

Requires a CD-Key or crack, which is not provided.

Installation is in English.. Though I seem to recall the ability to other install language packs.. But I'm not sure

Not a 64bit installation

This was downloaded as a student copy. I would strongly advise that you do not use this for commercial purposes.
